{
  "stem": "22582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and there were all kind of places that they were repairing things and washing, big laundry, and-- and preparing for-- for transport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was one of the people, 12 people, loading the trains where the merchandise were going out to the train and-- and-- or cleaning up or taking out the furniture from that apartments and later loading to the trains.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything to Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Clean things, and the apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You clean up the apartment, naturally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then-- then once the-- the apartments were cleaned, [? when ?] the sections would [? ghetto, ?] they-- they made it [? by ?] smaller ghettos.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how it-- that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this period was very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember this-- this period left a very bad time, a very bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, you saw a lot of tragic things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A lot of people were, when they made the ghetto smaller, a lot of people were hiding in the apartments, in the houses.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were bringing those people through, I remember, like through Polish section, because the sections were-- in Polish sections.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember people were found while-- I remember 11 or 12 people, they took it by the rope and like-- like-- like-- and they were leading them by the neck, one bound to another one, through the streets.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I guess that's to show people within Poland, the Polish people, to-- to be careful and not to-- not to-- to take any people to hide.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "To-- to-- to-- and they brought them over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, that was a daily appearance, daily things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's not something once happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It happened almost every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we have on this square, they built as like a pyre.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
